{"tid":1267422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政府咁想升旗，點解要阻住佢升？","createTime":"2019-06-30T00:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T01:30:07.000Z","uid":137721,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33568ca33b19f062ada8fccb7bfb60e8dc30b33e","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:51:20.000Z","msg":"71回歸呢個咁值得記念既日子<br />\n大家不但止唔可以阻住升旗儀式，仲應該協助個儀式!!<br />\n<br />\n雖然講就咁講<br />\n我明白大家痛恨外國勢力亂中禍港<br />\n但愛黨愛國既大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千祈唔好係人地領事館升上中國國旗</span></strong><br />\n咁樣只會令到國家敵立更加多既敵人<br />\n<br />\n更加要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>提防示威者假扮愛黨愛國人士亂中禍港</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再講搞人地領事館就同宣戰無分別<br />\n八國聯軍既歷史已經話左俾我地聽<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>搞人領事館只會令人出師有名</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家千祈唔好做</span>"},{"pid":"85e585d2a5c2ccf0bf0b7ef5830c298671b81715","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"強烈抗議外國勢力搧動港人搞亂國家"},{"pid":"63416154356e21cf471c44d75d5198e98c6f8edf","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:54:39.000Z","msg":"答我啦廢青"},{"pid":"f914de8de3163805fde0ec83e9b6ae2b4c2a8dfb","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:55:46.000Z","msg":"對於廢青打著中國旗號反中國表示強烈不滿"},{"pid":"b69f30958dcd9ff6de5b5986f3091016fffe50fa","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:58:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾淨係識負皮"},{"pid":"f045d1b922cd1c146deb957ca05b79c61d614a29","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:59:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b0f42129e06b52fb6f726a8cf7a53b1ee57ec76","tid":1267422,"uid":137721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aa4ff2fb7d010e3cfae